                        <interp inst="t18481218-name-202" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH EMMETT</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">policeman, N</hi> 351). I stopped the prisoner about half a mile from the prosecutor's shop, with this shawl under his coat.</p>
